card_text: (This card is always treated as an "Inzektor" card.)$NSend 1 other "Inzektor" card from your hand or face-up field to the GY, then activate 1 of these effects;$N●Choose 1 "Inzektor" monster from your Deck and either Special Summon it, or equip it to 1 "Inzektor" monster you control.$N●Equip 1 "Inzektor" Equip Spell from your Deck to 1 "Inzektor" monster you control.$NYou can only activate 1 "Zektrike Kou-ou" per turn.
